===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-pavilion.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
'''pavilion''' (''plural:'' '''[[pavilions]]''')

# an [[ornate]] [[tent]]
# a [[light]] [[roofed]] [[structure]] used as a [[shelter]] in a [[public]] [[place]]
# a structure, sometimes [[temporary]], [[erect]]ed to [[house]] [[exhibit]]s at a [[fair]], etc
#{{cricket}} the [[building]] where the [[player]]s change clothes, wait to bat, and eat their meals
# the [[lower]] [[surface]] of a [[brilliant-cut]] [[gemstone]]
#the [[cartiliginous]] part of the [[outer ear]]

====Synonyms====
*(''part of ear''): [[auricle]], [[pinna]]<!--Note: "external ear" and "outer ear" are not synonyms as they include non-cartiliginous parts too-->

